6.4 Accessibility

Keyboard navigation: Tab through hook types, Enter to select/deselect
Screen reader announcements: "Selected unexpected hook type", "Generated 3 hooks"
Focus indicators: Clear visual focus rings on all interactive elements
ARIA labels: All buttons and controls properly labeled
Color contrast: Text meets WCAG AA standards (4.5:1) on all backgrounds
Skip links: "Skip to generated hooks" link when results load

6.5 Micro-interactions

Selection animation: Checkboxes animate with smooth check transition
Card hover: Subtle lift (translateY: -2px) and shadow enhancement
Generate button pulse: Gentle pulse animation when enabled
Hook card entry: Stagger animation (each card fades in with 100ms delay)
Edit mode: Smooth height transition when card expands
Copy-to-clipboard: Visual confirmation toast when hook is copied

